This complete system requires @astrify/react-s3-upload and sonner to be installed:

```bash
npm install @astrify/react-s3-upload sonner
```

Then wrap your app with the FileUploadProvider and add the Toaster:

```tsx
import { FileUploadProvider } from '@astrify/react-s3-upload';
import { Toaster } from 'sonner';

function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <FileUploadProvider config={{
        signedStorageUrl: '/api/signed-storage-url',
        maxFiles: 10,
        maxSize: 50 * 1024 * 1024
      }}>
        {/* Your components */}
      </FileUploadProvider>
      <Toaster position="bottom-right" richColors />
    </>
  );
}
```
